6*****CMD
difference between RUN And CMD is 
 run is during the image creation
 cmd is running on the container (after the base image is created)
 CMD ["/usr/sbin/apache2ctl","-D","FOREGROUND"]

****CMD u dont need to run with /bin/bash as it will be runnning in daemon




